stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle
    Idle --> Running : start
    Running --> Idle : stop
    Running --> Error : fail
    Error --> Idle : reset
    state fork1 <<fork>>
    state join1 <<join>>
    state choice1 <<choice>>
    Running --> fork1
    fork1 --> Logging
    fork1 --> Metrics
    Logging --> join1
    Metrics --> join1
    join1 --> Done
    Done --> choice1
    choice1 --> Idle : retry
    choice1 --> [*] : exit
